    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game about energy, flesh and what's in between. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/f36b0eac17013bd29b7e6883a5fa0f7c.poster.avif?t=1767739116\" width=640 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/f36b0eac17013bd29b7e6883a5fa0f7c.webm?t=1767739116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/f36b0eac17013bd29b7e6883a5fa0f7c.mp4?t=1767739116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in strategic, turn-based battles where every decision counts. Collect and equip powerful weapons, armor, and relics to shape your character. Recruit and lead your party to triumph against the stars and the ocean. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>! Around you, the air is filled with powerful entities, both ancient and malevolent. Commune with these beings to harness their powers !</i> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/bd59d00cdd51f14681fab0876562bc12.poster.avif?t=1767739116\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/bd59d00cdd51f14681fab0876562bc12.webm?t=1767739116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029380/extras/bd59d00cdd51f14681fab0876562bc12.mp4?t=1767739116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through various landscapes, from lush forests to treacherous caves and ancient cities. Each location offers unique challenges, secrets, and opportunities. Uncover the lore of these lands through an immersive dialogue system. You can befriend, betray, or outwit those you meet.</p>",
